{"tid":611076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★勞工假返工沒怨言  葉先生：需要供樓25年 需要辛勤工作","createTime":"2018-03-30T15:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T10:59:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"afa2cdd36483a85b3c418a81be8901849bc21b5a","tid":611076,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">與母抽中居屋：需要辛勤工作供樓<br />\n</span><br />\n年約30歲的葉先生從前任職售貨員，最近兩年轉為送貨工人，他在旺角工作時說，每周工作6天，只有周日放假。對於要在公眾假期上班，他表示早已習慣，未有特別感到不快，但看見朋友可以放假，並將玩樂相片放上FB「放閃」，自己總會有點羨慕。<br />\n<br />\n對於現時的工作，他表示工作穩定，每天早上8時上班，工作至傍晚6時，月入2萬多元，即使需要於｢紅日｣工作，但由於應徵時已經知道，故早有心理準備，更認為較以往做售貨員時的輪更制好。他續稱，現時與母親同住，早前成功｢抽中｣居屋，預計<span style=\"color: red;\">需要供樓25年，所以需要辛勤工作，對工作沒有太大怨言。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1320074/org/fba641f6de5f0ccb07bc295d282d1568.jpg/IlCBBCQEAxN_-14WETkmPBgxYOm0IrkfcVR4YXFUeGE?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1320074%2Forg%2Ffba641f6de5f0ccb07bc295d282d1568.jpg%2FIlCBBCQEAxN_-14WETkmPBgxYOm0IrkfcVR4YXFUeGE%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=1ac21478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/173532/%E5%BE%A9%E6%B4%BB%E7%AF%80-%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E8%97%8D%E9%A0%98%E7%B4%85%E6%97%A5%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD-%E9%80%81%E8%B2%A8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA-%E7%BE%A8%E6%85%95%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8E%BB%E7%8E%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F173532%2F%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%2597%258D%25E9%25A0%2598%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258F%25AD-%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%25BE%25A8%25E6%2585%2595%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%258E%